$interpreted: Devious: Let me save you from your wavering.
Devious: After the proclamation ceremony, when she's leaving the desert, I'll let her rest in peace forever. No one will ever know...
Andrew: ...No.
Devious: Andrew...sir?
Andrew: I must keep my promise and let her leave peacefully.
Devious: Absolutely not. The risk is too——
Andrew: High Priest, you're the most conservative snake I've ever met...and the most pious.
Andrew: Do you remember what you taught me when I was a little child?
Devious: ......
Andrew: Legend has it that when the world was created, the desert was blocked off by a barrier of wind, and there was no water nor vegetation.
Andrew: The Snake God used his body to smash the barrier, while the Snake Goddess bit her own flesh to feed us lowly ones her flesh and blood.
Andrew: Once the God and Goddess died, the barrier subsided and the snake people moved to a lush land to survive.
Andrew: Thereby becoming our ancestors.
Andrew: We believe that justice is the interest of the stronger, yet the one who is eaten is the Snake God and Goddess.
Andrew: What you told me about the strong is quite different from the real world.
Andrew: In the Desert Kingdom, the king is the weakest of them all.
Andrew: When the citizens need something, both family and one's own flesh are required to be sacrificed for the snake people.
Andrew: When Diana leaves, she abandons her status as a member of the Gomez family and will become an orphan of the Desert Kingdom.
Andrew: As King, is there nothing I can offer to her to eat?
Devious: I was not clear at the time...Andrew, listen to me...
Devious: What was that...who's there?
Clover: ...Shattered...is that a Rune? What the humans use...?
Lazer: When I gave you the Clover Crystal, I locked it with a Rune.
Lazer: I knew you'd carry it with you. Just in case, I could unlock it from afar and attack a target close to you.
Clover: You never planned on telling me.
Lazer: I feared that you would misunderstand. It seems I was correct. In any case, you're safe.
Clover: ...Safe!? You think now I'm safe!?
Clover: Do you see these crystals!? They're all shattered!! I'm shattered!!!
Clover: From now on there is no Clover, only Diana!
Lazer: ......
Lazer: I'm not concerned about that, child.
Clover: I haven't finished. Do not leave! You are not permitted to leave!
Clover: You can't keep doing this!
Lazer: Fine. This will be the last time. You must rest...
Clover: I'm not finished!!!!!!! AHHHHHHHH!!!!!
Lazer: Keep it down! It's danger——
Clover: You killed the wrong snake! Andrew shouldn't have died!
Lazer: ...You may kill me as a punishment. But you must live.
Clover: ......
Diana: I've had enough.
Diana: As you wished, I will become Diana.
Diana: You took Andrew's life, and with it...Clover's.
Diana: I will pay the price for what you have done to this country.
Lazer: ...Yes, your Majesty, my Queen.
